name: Playful Frostkin

name: Plump Jelly

name: Porcupette

name: Poro

name: Puddle Terror

name: Race MiniZep

name: Red Cricket

name: Restored Revenant

name: River Calf

name: Rocket Chicken
source: |cFFFFD200Trading Card Game:|r March of the Legion

name: Rooter

name: Rotten Little Helper

name: Royal Peachick

name: Ruby Droplet

name: Sanctum Cub

name: Sand Scarab

name: Savage Cub

name: Scabby

description: He's one cowardly companion, because he's got no guts...
name: Scraps

description: Scuttle was named after the ships he destroys, not his movement patterns, and don't you forget it.
name: Scuttle

description: The sea calf has a natural affinity for balancing things.
name: Sea Calf

name: Searing Scorchling

name: Sen'jin Fetish

name: Sentinel's Companion

name: Sewer-Pipe Jelly

name: Shadow

name: Shard of Cyrukh

name: Sinister Squashling

name: Sir Snips

name: Sister of Temptation

name: Sky Fry

name: Sky Lantern

name: Sky-Bo

name: Skyhorn Nestling

name: Snapper

name: Snort

name: Snowy Panda
